{"tid":316400,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"(幫手解決左個問題先好sale野) 網上行冷靜期","createTime":"2017-07-10T16:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T09:39:19.000Z","uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77a8ae92e7d12ceba6eb8ff9df31698d05583786","tid":316400,"uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"簡短: <br />\n網上行就完約, 但今日口頭續左, 點先可以唔賠錢cut左佢?<br />\n<br />\n詳細: <br />\n網上行阿爸申請的, 但佢係水魚, 一路食貴plan<br />\n幾年前就完約, 我叫佢cut, 佢唔理, 照做水魚<br />\n到前幾日, 我叫佢cut, 我自己比錢, 申請另一間<br />\n到今日阿媽同我講, 佢因為sales話平d比佢, 所以又續左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n詳細我冇問, 因為肯定又係水魚plan<br />\n因為我想自己申請plan(以後唔洗經佢手), 同想升上1000MB (而家得100M), 所以想叫佢自己cut左pccw個邊佢<br />\n上網搵過資料見到續約應該都有冷靜期, 但詳細唔清楚, 有冇巴打/sales知點cut, thx<br />\n<br />\n幫手cut到幫襯你又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19255eb14c4f6562657e755532902fb427fb5edd","tid":316400,"uid":126478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7899c4faed1b7372b45adbf403f001fab5ddc52","tid":316400,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"Netvigator續約冇冷靜期"},{"pid":"ef91928b7c4e95bf45b810ffc469e2b2eecb4e7f","tid":316400,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:40:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec160eeea72776395a3f2066df40cb1664edcf5","tid":316400,"uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Netvigator續約冇冷靜期</blockquote><br />\n咁除左硬食仲可以點, cut 係唔係要賠足全數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw, 如果我唔鬼理佢, 直接申請過睇二間(比2間既錢)會唔會有問題, 例如駁線之類? <br />\n真係唔想理條on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2bf48f37d9ec0f2bdf23e5a0c363d24a6bc1c0","tid":316400,"uid":126478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:34:41.000Z